high_descs: Turn around and face the fridge
Open the bottom door of the fridge
Grab a tomato from the fridge and walk towards the microwave
Brown the tomato in the microwave and then grab the tomato
Walk to the right of the sink counter and look for the trash bin
Place the tomato inside the trash bin.
Turn to your right and walk to the front of the fridge so you are facing it.
Open the fridge and pick up the tomato to the right of the top shelf.
Turn around and walk to the counter and then turn right and walk so you are in front of the stove top.
Put the tomato in the microwave, cook it and take it back out.
Now walk to the far side of the room turning left when you hit the dining room table and stand in front of the garbage.
Put the tomato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato in the microwave before placing it in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn around and walk the fridge.
Take the tomato out of the fridge.
Turn around and veer right to the stove.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn around a veer left. Walk to the back left corner and turn around.
Place the tomato in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the trash.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge
Take a tomato out of the fridge
Turn around and go to the counter then turn right and go to the stove
Put the tomato in the microwave and microwave it then take the tomato out of the microwave
Turn to the right, then turn right again and go to the far wall and turn left and go to the garbage can
Put the tomato in the garbage can
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato in the garbage can

high_descs: Move across the room to the refrigerator.
Open the door and take the tomato off of the top shelf.  Close the door.
Move across the room to the microwave.
Place the tomato inside the microwave and turn it on to cook the tomato.  Remove the tomato from the microwave.
Move across the room to the silver trash bin that is sitting by the counter.
Put the tomato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato in the microwave to be placed into the trash bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the out of the tomato fridge, then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn right and walk up to the oven and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato inside, then close the microwave door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the tomato then close the door.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the small silver bin on the ground to the next of the counter.
Put the heated tomato in the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in a silver bin.
